{"tid":547682,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[求教]機場抄牌","createTime":"2018-02-01T16:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-06T14:55:09.000Z","uid":53234,"like":0,"dislike":39,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"97368872037584290de1c9f2866019ea91ac9de9","tid":547682,"uid":53234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T16:27:13.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我有個friend喺落客區上客。有個唔係差佬嘅督導員見到後點佢拍埋一邊，當時佢喺企喺架車前面。我個friend無理佢，踩油走人，個督導員嚇一嚇縮開咗。跟住我個friend就走咗人喇。佢而家想知個督導員會唔會挖到佢? 督導員唔係差人，有冇權告佢? 有冇巴打有類似經驗可以分享吓?"},{"pid":"955a786f4cb93f5bf0170e815956de8293efb279","tid":547682,"uid":92664,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"記得車牌告危駕都似<br />\n個到只可以落客,唔可以上客, 我記得"},{"pid":"271ad7c483ba571d90cc6d19d1b08fe2649f0536","tid":547682,"uid":53234,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"955a786f4cb93f5bf0170e815956de8293efb279","tid":547682,"uid":92664,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"記得車牌告危駕都似<br />\n個到只可以落客,唔可以上客, 我記得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"但係唔係差人喎，有權咩? 除非佢報警"},{"pid":"8ba71289c8b7fa615818a707ff7ad485a01acab4","tid":547682,"uid":6636,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"271ad7c483ba571d90cc6d19d1b08fe2649f0536","tid":547682,"uid":53234,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"955a786f4cb93f5bf0170e815956de8293efb279","tid":547682,"uid":92664,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T16:48:36.000Z","msg":"記得車牌告危駕都似<br />\n個到只可以落客,唔可以上客, 我記得"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"但係唔係差人喎，有權咩? 除非佢報警"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:08:56.000Z","msg":"你自己都答咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你係犯法嘅話邊個都可以告你㗎啦"},{"pid":"0bba0ec1dbc6e2c64cbae40ab28172805c8a336f","tid":547682,"uid":92664,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"271ad7c483ba571d90cc6d19d1b08fe2649f0536","tid":547682,"uid":53234,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"quote":{"pid":"9