By":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:52:36.000Z","msg":"係掛，據我所知就一定唔係差人"},{"pid":"19913fc958553a69f9d5b9be45325841e87ddc87","tid":547682,"uid":16676,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:56:33.000Z","msg":"乜野人黎, 竟然話機場島唔會有咖啡仔執法<br />\n只有AA 先管得既説話... 我諗avseco 先真係唔會理<br />\n<br />\n我諗無腦既都講唔出呢d 野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係T1 個落客區先成日見佢地係果度當更<br />\n<br />\n反而交通警比較少 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咖啡仔就係專捉呢樣, 佢唔挖你出黎, 無可能囉<br />\n有晒CCTV, 仲要拒捕, 隨時立功添, 點會放過你呢條水魚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"273795cef6374f453dd0750a6351f98d3bdbd78b","tid":547682,"uid":16676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfca43705204463cb42e3b0773c71c27ba2ddedb","tid":547682,"uid":53234,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"cc9bc1ec755c06974d6506011c1407e3fc04f46b","tid":547682,"uid":58209,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:18:13.000Z","msg":"你知唔知咖啡仔係隸屬交通部？<br />\n同大sir開句聲要做你有幾難<br />\n等收信 柒頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T17:37:28.000Z","msg":"機場係run by 機管局, 你幾時見過機場有咖啡仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  柒頭"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-01T18:01:30.000Z","msg":"果個位係黑點<br />\n成日日抖有人係果度當更, 唔比人泊車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日要係果度趕車, 廢事排晒隊<br />\n果度一塞就會塞埋裡面巴士線<br />\n而且有時有d 懵丙揸左架車入埋面條線落客<br />\n最多油水, 最易開告票既地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6b91b6426be410f0f01cb3595e94af3e4cc719","tid":547682,"uid":26811,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"e5b175b5f2b505a43925876743f8a6c8d87591f1","tid":547682,"uid":6778,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"18d992b0de0109a9304e18186bab834e03647858","tid":547682,"uid":6